article_title: TV networks owned by Chattanooga multimillionaires could head to auction block

article_metadata.description: The broadcast TV networks owned by Chattanooga multimillionaires Henry Luken and Forrest Preston could go to the highest bidder following a legal setback in in Arkansas, as the entrepreneur prepares to appeal his case before a federal appellate court.
